<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
      .header { background-color: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 20px; }
      .alert-box { background-color: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #dc2626; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .stats { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üö® AI Spending Limit Exceeded</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      
      <p>Your workspace "<strong><%= @workspace.name %></strong>" has exceeded its <%= @limit_type %> AI spending limit.</p>
      
      <div class="alert-box">
        <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Spending Alert Details</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Limit Type:</strong> <%= @limit_type.humanize %></li>
          <li><strong>Limit Amount:</strong> $<%= sprintf('%.2f', @limit_amount) %></li>
          <li><strong>Current Spend:</strong> $<%= sprintf('%.2f', @current_spend) %></li>
          <li><strong>Percentage:</strong> <%= @percentage %>% of limit</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="stats">
        <h3>üìä What this means:</h3>
        <p>Your workspace has reached <strong><%= @percentage %>%</strong> of its <%= @limit_type %> spending limit for AI services. This includes costs from language model requests, embeddings, and other AI-powered features.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Recommended Actions:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Review your AI usage patterns and optimize where possible</li>
          <li>Consider adjusting your routing policies to use more cost-effective models</li>
          <li>Increase your spending limits if this usage level is expected</li>
          <li>Monitor individual request costs and implement tighter cost controls</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <p>You can review your AI spending and adjust limits in your workspace settings.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The AI Cost Monitoring System</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated notification from your AI cost monitoring system.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>